                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9509" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">OB-0426</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1157 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中正和荣：传统文化赋能尔目文旅集团战略转型的“道-法-术”</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">ZhongZheng HeRong: Empowering the Strategic Transformation of Ermu Cultural and Tourism Group with Traditional Culture Through &quot;Dao Fa Shu&quot;</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">赵航，郭剑英、谢海涛，杨淇深</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南京林业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">江苏尔目文化旅游发展集团</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">党群部门/思想政治工作部门/企业文化部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业文化；中国传统文化；文化赋能</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"> Corporate Culture, Traditional Chinese Culture, Cultural Empowering</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">江苏尔目文化旅游发展集团（简称尔目文旅）以中国传统文化促进组织能力转变，从而实现从“文旅规划设计服务”向“规划设计与运营一体化服务”的战略转型。在这个过程中，尔目文旅重塑使命和愿景，以“大中至正，和荣共生”为核心发展理念，树立了“行明德，正人本”的价值观和相应的服务理念与行为准则，建立完整的文化体系。而后通过内修德行，外塑形象，“道-法-术”一以贯之的文化建设，建立文化认同，推动知行合一，借助于文化的导向、激励、凝聚、约束和辐射等功能，构建共生共赢的社会生态，打造成为文旅全产业链服务机构。案例从战略转型的需要出发，描述了传统文化在尔目文旅构建与落地的全过程，以期解构企业文化，明晰文化建设的过程，使学生能更深入的理解文化对战略的赋能机制。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Jiangsu Ermu Culture and Tourism Development Group (referred to as Ermu Culture and Tourism Group) promotes organizational capacity transformation through traditional Chinese culture, thereby achieving a strategic transformation from &quot;cultural tourism planning and design services&quot; to &quot;integrated planning, design, and operation services&quot;. In this process, Ermu Culture and Tourism Group has reshaped its mission and vision, with the core development concept of &quot;harmony and prosperity&quot;, established the values of &quot;moral integrity and human centeredness&quot;, and corresponding service concepts and codes of conduct, and established a complete cultural system. Then, through the internal cultivation of moral character, external shaping of image, and the consistent cultural construction of &quot;Dao Fa Shu&quot;, cultural identity is established, and the integration of knowledge and action is promoted. With the guidance, motivation, cohesion, restraint, and radiation of culture, a symbiotic and win-win social ecology is constructed, and it is built into a cultural tourism industry chain service institution. Starting from the need for strategic transformation, this case describes the entire process of traditional culture in the construction and implementation of Ermu Culture and Tourism Group, aiming to deconstruct corporate culture, clarify the process of cultural construction, and enable students to have a deeper understanding of the empowering mechanism of culture on strategy.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《组织行为学》、《企业文化》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业文化的内涵与结构；企业文化的认知与认同机制；企业文化的落地与行为强化机制；企业文化的功能及其对战略的赋能机制</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-03</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
